card_text: If you control no monsters: Activate 1 of the following effects; also for the rest of this turn after this card resolves, you cannot Special Summon monsters, except "Yosenju" monsters.$N●Add 1 Level 5 or higher "Yosenju" monster from your Deck to your hand.$N●Place 1 "Yosenju Shinchu L" and 1 "Yosenju Shinchu R" from your Deck in your Pendulum Zones, but destroy them during your opponent's next End Phase.
